Tartar
sprang
down
the
pavement
towards
the
gate,
bellowing
avec
explosion.
His
mistress
quietly
opened
the
glass
door,
and
stepped
out
chirruping
to
him.
His
bellow
was
already
silenced,
and
he
was
lifting
up
his
huge,
blunt,
stupid
head
to
the
new
callers
to
be
