"What!
Tartar,
Tartar!"
said
a
cheery,
rather
boyish
voice,
"don't
you
know
us?
Good
morning,
old
boy!"
And
little
Mr.
Sweeting,
whose
conscious
good
nature
made
him
comparatively
fearless
of
man,
woman,
child,
or
